{
  "sourceLanguage": "en",
  "strings": {
    "Both models run locally with similar speed, download size, and memory use. No API key is required.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Beide Modelle laufen lokal und haben eine ähnliche Geschwindigkeit, Downloadgröße und Speichernutzung. Es ist kein API-Schlüssel erforderlich."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "どちらのモデルもローカルで動作し、速度、ダウンロードサイズ、メモリ使用量はほぼ同じです。APIキーは不要です。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "CTC model (~100 MB) - downloads automatically on first use, or:": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "CTC-Modell (~100 MB) - wird automatisch beim ersten Gebrauch geladen, oder:"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "CTCモデル (~100 MB) - 最初に使用するときに自動で読み込まれます。または:"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Download & Load": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Laden & Aktivieren"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "読み込み & 有効化"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Download Now": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jetzt herunterladen"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "今すぐダウンロード"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Done": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fertig"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "完了"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Downloading CTC model...": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "CTC-Modell wird heruntergeladen..."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "CTCモデルがダウンロード中..."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Enable Vocabulary Boosting": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vokabel-Boosting aktivieren"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "語彙ブーストを有効化"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Improves recognition of custom terms from your Dictionary using a secondary CTC model.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Verbessert die Erkennung von Fachbegriffen aus dem Wörterbuch mittels eines sekundären CTC-Modells."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "辞書の専門用語の認識を、セカンダリCTCモデルにより向上させます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Runs a second local speech model to detect dictionary terms. This can improve names and technical vocabulary, but uses more processing time on long dictations. Leise prepares completed audio windows while you speak to reduce the wait after stopping.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Verwendet ein zweites lokales Sprachmodell, um Wörterbuchbegriffe zu erkennen. Das kann Namen und Fachbegriffe verbessern, benötigt bei langen Diktaten aber mehr Rechenzeit. Leise bereitet abgeschlossene Audioabschnitte bereits während des Sprechens vor, um die Wartezeit nach dem Beenden zu verkürzen."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "辞書用語を検出するために、2つ目のローカル音声モデルを使用します。名前や専門用語の認識を改善できますが、長い音声入力では処理時間が増えます。Leiseは停止後の待ち時間を短縮するため、話している間に完了済みの音声区間を準備します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hugging Face Token": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hugging Face Token"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Hugging Faceトークン"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Invalid Hugging Face Token": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ungültiger Hugging Face Token"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "無効なHugging Faceトークン"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Model Version": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Modellversion"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "モデルバージョン"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Best for English-only dictation. V2 generally has higher English recall. Choose V3 if you dictate in another language.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Am besten für ausschließlich englische Diktate. V2 erzielt bei Englisch im Allgemeinen eine höhere Erkennungsrate. Wähle V3, wenn du in einer anderen Sprache diktierst."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "英語のみの音声入力に最適です。V2は一般に英語の認識率が高くなります。他の言語で音声入力する場合はV3を選んでください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Recommended for most users. V3 supports 25 European languages, including English and German. Choose V2 only for English-only dictation.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Für die meisten Benutzer empfohlen. V3 unterstützt 25 europäische Sprachen, darunter Englisch und Deutsch. Wähle V2 nur für ausschließlich englische Diktate."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ほとんどのユーザーに推奨します。V3は英語とドイツ語を含む25のヨーロッパ言語に対応しています。英語のみの音声入力ではV2を選択できます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Optional. Increases download rate limits. Free at huggingface.co/settings/tokens": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Optional. Erhöht die Download-Rate-Limits. Kostenlos unter huggingface.co/settings/tokens"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "任意です。ダウンロードのレート制限を緩和できます。huggingface.co/settings/tokens で無料作成できます"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Ready - %lld terms loaded": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Bereit - %lld Begriffe geladen"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "準備完了 - %lld語読み込まれました"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Ready - add terms in Dictionary settings": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Bereit - Begriffe in Wörterbuch-Einstellungen hinzufügen"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "準備完了 - 辞書設定で語を追加"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Remove": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Entfernen"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "削除"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Retry": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Erneut versuchen"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "再試行"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Save": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Speichern"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "保存"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Unload": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Deaktivieren"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "無効化"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Valid Hugging Face Token": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Gültiger Hugging Face Token"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "有効なHugging Faceトークン"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Validating token...": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Token wird geprüft..."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "トークンを検証中..."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Vocabulary Boosting": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Vokabel-Boosting"
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "語彙ブースト"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "version": "1.0"
}
